OL,3,CSwimmers fear for their health as
OL,4,Creport reveals Devon rivers are
OL,5,C'dangerously polluted'
OL,7,FWatch Sam Blackledge's report
OL,9,FTwo major rivers in Devon which are
OL,10,Fpopular with wild swimmers are
OL,11,Fdangerously polluted, according to a
OL,12,Fnew report.Research from Surfers
OL,13,FAgainst Sewage shows the River Dart
OL,14,Fand the River Erme contain high
OL,15,Flevels of bacteria. The campaign
OL,16,Fgroup says this is caused by sewage
OL,17,Fand water run off from farms.
OL,19,FCampaigners want water companies and
OL,20,Fthe government to take urgent action.
